  <brief_title>Analysis of Hospitalizations One Year After Acts of CAG and PCI in the Aquitaine région - ACIRA Register Data Analysis</brief_title>
  <acronym>ACIRA-REHOSP</acronym>
  <official_title>Frequency and Characteristics of Rehospitalizations During One Year After Percutaneous Coronary Intervention and Coronary Angiography - Results of the ACIRA Registry, Aquitaine Region</official_title>
